<p>Welcome to the ISGA walkthrough.  These prompts will 
be present throughout the pipeline building experience.  They are intended 
to provided interactive guidance as well as visual prompts.  They can be turned off
at any time by clicking the Hide Walkthrough link in the upper right of the navigation 
menu.  They can also be permanantely disabled by editing your <a class="normal" href="/Account/EditMyDetails">
Account Details</a>.</p>

<p>To begin building and customizing a pipeline, please hover over
<span class="highlight">Build Pipelines</span> on the drop down menu 
and click a pipeline from the list.  You will be taken to the overview 
page for the pipeline.  From there you will be able to choose to either 
edit and customize the pipeline or run it using default values.</p>
</div></div></div>
